  "detailed_description": "STREAM WAR is an streaming-based game that allows viewers of live broadcasts to participate through comments.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deathmatch Mode</h2>A new mode, Deathmatch Mode, has been added. In this mode, viewers can participate by using the \"!join\" command while watching the stream on twitch.tv. Characters with the names of participating viewers will fight with weapons until only one person remains.<br>The maximum number of participating viewers depends on the playing environment and can be specified in the tens of thousands. Enjoy Deathmatch Mode with a large number of viewers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/b92810cf11937e57d812586d970b1246.avif?t=1758075389\" width=306 height=158 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team Mode </h2>Streamers can link their Twitch account to this game with one click.<br>Viewers join this game by commands in twitch comments to spawn characters. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/755f95796a2611140f6d40739660e013.avif?t=1758075389\" width=502 height=198 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/1db9068cba51b2692f17fde61c26585d.avif?t=1758075389\" width=366 height=122 /></span><br><br>A character with viewer's name will spawn when they join.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/ba484d3062ce241f94c4a74292cfa263.avif?t=1758075389\" width=438 height=200 /></span><br><br>Each teams fight until one of them is wiped out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/f0ce2521ce6ace13a8d6f2f0a8b9403d.poster.avif?t=1758075389\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/f0ce2521ce6ace13a8d6f2f0a8b9403d.webm?t=1758075389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/f0ce2521ce6ace13a8d6f2f0a8b9403d.mp4?t=1758075389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/b09be27ca95b783340babf29a7d6188d.avif?t=1758075389\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><br>Viewers can also use the !bomb command to drop bombs on the battlefield during combat and the !cam command to change viewpoint. <br>Winning viewers can increase their in-game points and compete for rankings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/0274b6cad46d7185dc08f99a889903ab.avif?t=1758075389\" width=600 height=230 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "STREAM WAR is an streaming-based game that allows viewers of live broadcasts to participate through comments.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deathmatch Mode</h2>A new mode, Deathmatch Mode, has been added. In this mode, viewers can participate by using the \"!join\" command while watching the stream on twitch.tv. Characters with the names of participating viewers will fight with weapons until only one person remains.<br>The maximum number of participating viewers depends on the playing environment and can be specified in the tens of thousands. Enjoy Deathmatch Mode with a large number of viewers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/b92810cf11937e57d812586d970b1246.avif?t=1758075389\" width=306 height=158 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team Mode </h2>Streamers can link their Twitch account to this game with one click.<br>Viewers join this game by commands in twitch comments to spawn characters. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/755f95796a2611140f6d40739660e013.avif?t=1758075389\" width=502 height=198 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/1db9068cba51b2692f17fde61c26585d.avif?t=1758075389\" width=366 height=122 /></span><br><br>A character with viewer's name will spawn when they join.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/ba484d3062ce241f94c4a74292cfa263.avif?t=1758075389\" width=438 height=200 /></span><br><br>Each teams fight until one of them is wiped out.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/f0ce2521ce6ace13a8d6f2f0a8b9403d.poster.avif?t=1758075389\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/f0ce2521ce6ace13a8d6f2f0a8b9403d.webm?t=1758075389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/f0ce2521ce6ace13a8d6f2f0a8b9403d.mp4?t=1758075389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/b09be27ca95b783340babf29a7d6188d.avif?t=1758075389\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><br>Viewers can also use the !bomb command to drop bombs on the battlefield during combat and the !cam command to change viewpoint. <br>Winning viewers can increase their in-game points and compete for rankings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016960/extras/0274b6cad46d7185dc08f99a889903ab.avif?t=1758075389\" width=600 height=230 /></span>",
